title: American horror story-Mallory’s magic
author: Darkmagicianmagi
comment: She always seemed more of an archangel type of character but coolest witch nonetheless
I wish they would've just made her like an angel or something. As much as i love her becoming the new supreme, i hated how it made Cordelia's reign so short

I honestly think Mallory is the reincarnation of Hecate! Hecate is the Goddess of Witchcraft and seems like it could be the base of Mallory's character! I think she isnt only a supreme but the goddess of witchcraft because Hecate believed that nothing ever truly dies, that everything is energy that gets passed onto the next.
Finally a truly kind and pure main character who survived.
She has magic we dont even see the supreme use are you sure shes 'only' a witch?
